         <abstract id="aspace_7da9ccf7efcf2d960798e2f7aacb10cd">The materials consist of photographs by C. B. Wells of the Yale residential colleges, various academic buildings, commencement 1936, and scenes of Yale and New Haven in winter during the 1930s. Included are photographs taken after the 1938 hurricane.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="dts_3a5a2c7c3583b6b5c992faee25551a39d8cad48b"
                      rules="aacr"
                      source="naf">
               <part>Wells, C. B.</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_dfd6443ee4e2f1ff99d2e9f0ac423c67">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-A (YRG 46-A), Records and materials broadly documenting Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_dc4d9ee4269d2db5d299d2342c88f82c">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>C. B. Wells Photographs of Yale (RU 639). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_1c9671714ef8f78fbbd38489446aab34">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_55ef3a2ade67a01e680678ba401797f0">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_75784649eab68dc9387f09a5e2356020">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs by C. B. Wells of the Yale residential colleges, various academic buildings, commencement 1936, and scenes of Yale and New Haven in winter during the 1930s. Included are photographs taken after the 1938 hurricane.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
